summaryProfile.longBusinessSummary: The fund seeks to achieve this objective by (1) creating an actively managed portfolio of equity securities comprised significantly of those included in the funds primary benchmark, the Nasdaq-100 Index (the Benchmark), and (2) through equity-linked notes (ELNs), selling call options with exposure to the Benchmark. It is non-diversified.
